+## Development stack
+
+Install the quality and test layer:
+
+```bash
+python -m pip install -e ".[dev]"
+pre-commit install
+python -m ruff check .
+python -m pytest
+```
+
+The core package remains dependency-free. Heavier capabilities are isolated in
+optional extras and do not become authoritative simply because they are
+installed:
+
+```bash
+python -m pip install -e ".[ingestion]"
+python -m pip install -e ".[memory-benchmark]"
+python -m pip install -e ".[agents]"
+python -m pip install -e ".[data-validation]"
+python -m pip install -e ".[data-ui]"
+```
+
+See [`docs/STACK.md`](docs/STACK.md) for the active stack, pilot gates, and
+deferred components.
+
 ## Trust boundary
 
 - The original source ZIP is preserved unchanged in a built record.
